; Coverage for report.cc limit conjunction with query

2024/01/01 Test1
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/01 Test2
    Expenses:Rent    $500.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --limit "amount > 0" Food
24-Jan-01 Test1                 Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
end test
